data.description: Welcome to your dream CUSTOM BUILT home in a prestigious gated community! IN-LAW APARTMENT Situated on a generous 1-acre corner lot, this home has 4 spacious bedrooms & 4  baths. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, featuring custom closets & an ensuite bath. The heart of this home is its stunning kitchen, complete with high-end appliances, including a gas cooktop that will delight any cooking enthusiast. The hardwood flooring throughout adds elegance to the living spaces. A in-law or nanny apartment includes a full kitchen. This self-contained space provides independent living options for extended family members. The layout offers a bonus room with a full bath, allowing for a fifth bedroom. Car enthusiasts will appreciate the the three-car garage, while the extended driveway provides ample parking. As you step outside, you'll be greeted by beautifully manicured grounds, offering plenty of room for outdoor entertaining.
